    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n4,8 \\sin\\left(\\frac{x}{9}\\right) = 3,6 \\Leftrightarrow \\sin\\left(\\frac{x}{9}\\right) = \\frac{3,6}{4,8} = 0,75 \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} \\frac{x}{9} = \\alpha + k2\\pi \\\\ \\frac{x}{9} = \\pi - \\alpha + k2\\pi \\end{cases} \\xrightarrow{k=0} \\begin{cases} x_1 = 9\\alpha \\\\ x_2 = 9(\\pi - \\alpha) \\end{cases} \\text{ (với } \\alpha \\approx 0,848\\dots \\text{ )}\n$$"
  },
  {
